text:
Summary by 9News It's been a stormy tail end to Christmas for the UK and Ireland, as the countries were hit by Storm Gerrit coming in from the Atlantic on Wednesday, bringing gale force winds and flooding in its wake.It caused havoc for aviation , with flights being cancelled across the countries.
